<P>
The Ansel Adams photograph, "Winter Sunrise, The Sierra Nevada, from Lone Pine, 
Calif.," shown as part of "Picturing California" (Sept. 3), reminded me of the 
absolutely magnificent views of that mountain range that can be seen from 
Highway 395 and the incredibly talented eye possessed by Adams. However, if the 
