<HEADLINE>
<P>
SEX AND IQ 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Constitution guarantees "life, liberty and the pursuit of happiness" to all 
citizens, not just those who are "normal" and thereby declare themselves 
non-handicapped and in some way superior. 
</P>
<P>
The mind-set that by virtue of a three-digit IQ we are dominant beings elected 
to oversee selective reproduction is not unlike the reasoning some half-century 
ago when only the blond and blue-eyed were to be allowed to procreate. 
</P>
<P>
As the writers of "L.A. Law" are so eloquently attempting to illustrate, the 
mentally retarded can be quite capable of making decisions regarding 
responsible sexual behavior if they are afforded the simple luxury of an 
unbiased education. 
</P>
<P>
Happily, some of my favorite people are dark-eyed. And some are mentally 
retarded. 
</P>
<P>
KATE CAHILL 
</P>
<P>
Palm Springs 
