GRAND OPENING: LA QUINTA HOMES OPEN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Rancho Ocotillo, a Williams Development Corp. project, is celebrating its grand 
opening this weekend. Thirty eight of 191 homes will be available for sale. 
</P>
<P>
The three-bedrooms homes each offer a convertible den and 2 1/2 bathrooms. They 
