<P>
DENTISTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I am writing in response to Calvin Trillin's column "A Costly Hour With Sweeney 
Todd, DDS," (Op-Ed Page, Nov. 14). 
</P>
