<HEADLINE>
<P>
PASTOR AND MISSION FUNDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I take exception to the implication The Times made in its Nov. 20 edition in 
which a picture of Pastor Chuck Swindoll was shown with a recap of the funds 
his mission was capable of generating in 1988. 
</P>
<P>
With all the "witch hunting" taking place in our society today regarding 
televangelism, I think it only fair that you write an article on the great 
things that "Insights for Living" has done for people throughout the world. 
</P>
<P>
If you're not willing to that, how about publishing the profits of the Los 
Angeles Times? 
</P>
<P>
RON KEE 
</P>
<P>
Garden Grove 
