USSR; BUSH, GEORGE; ARMS CONTROL; MILITARY FORCE REDUCTIONS; STRATEGIC ARMS 
REDUCTION TALKS; USSR -- ARMED FORCES -- EUROPE; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES 
-- EUROPE 
</P>
