</P>
</TEXT>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Chart, Political Contributions, Los Angeles Times; Photo, Democratic Assembly 
candidate Jerry Yudelson, left, is enthusiastic, current county party Chairman 
Michael Balmages is optimistic and former chairman John Hanna is philosophic 
about party prospects. Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
DEMOCRATIC PARTY (ORANGE COUNTY); POLITICAL ACTIVISM; REPUBLICAN PARTY (ORANGE 
